{
  "stem": "3855.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that is how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one is amazed that, despite the fact that Austria was 98% Catholic-- the number of Jews among 6 million was 200,000, a small percentage and very few Protestants-- that they went so overboard for Hitler.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's an interesting phenomenon because it's really the antithesis of Catholicism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler was really bound to reinstitute the old German gods, Wotan and Freyr, Loki, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was really his thrust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was located in the Seitenstettenstrasse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called the Seitenstetten Temple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the 1st district.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was probably the number one synagogue in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a beautiful building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You go in there now, it's a magnificent building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A huge rotunda with columns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was back there, some years back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seitenstetten.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-E-I-T-E-N-S-T-E-double T-E-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's the same as the street that it was on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother and I both were bar mitzvahed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a tradition, regardless of whether the family was very religious or not, because it was a-- an impetus for the relatives-- in our case, from Czechoslovakia-- to come down there for that occasion and see everybody and bring the obligatory Omega watch, which I still have.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the chief rabbi in Vienna at that time was Oberrabbiner-- top rabbi-- Chayes--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--who was really well-known in central Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was esteemed as a savant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C-H-A-Y-E-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really cannot answer that question, but I don't think there was a father by the name of Chayes before him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't hear that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I presume there, it was more by knowledge and learning and the esteem that he was able to garner as he climbed up in the hierarchy.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
